Disrespect to the environment!
Jul 2016 ‚Ä¢ Couples
It is a pity to see one of the natural wonders of the world so polluted and unprotected by the government.
There are lots of plastic bags, plastic bottles and other kind of rubbish floating in the water. Imagine kayaking or swimming in such a water! When you go for a visit to a Cave or an island, it is full of garbage too: plastic bottles everywhere, different kind of food waste.
It seems that the government doesn't care in taking any action to protect or at least clean the area! It is just a source of money.
I think places like that should be avoided by tourists as sign of protest for a disrespect to the environment. Never again!
